title: Seth Meyers & Brad Paisley (Podcast Exclusive)
description:
In a conversation recorded exclusively for the Late Night Podcast, Seth and his friend, country star Brad Paisley, discuss how Brad ended up as a surprise musical guest at Seth's wedding, their shared love of comedy, why Seth's father-in-law is Brad's biggest fan and more.
Following their chat, you'll hear Brad's appearance on Late Night.
